column4: This is ASOS DESIGN - your go-to for all the latest trends
Your go-anywhere lace-up trainers have received a few sartorial updates. Side stripes offer an athletic aesthetic and a contrasting toe panel adds extra interest. Comfortable and seriously stylish

Meet the Luca, our take on the timeless penny loafer. Details like a classic penny bridge, supple full-grain leather, and a sleek toe shape provide everything you need in a loafer, and more. An instant upgrade to your everyday attire.
